Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------MAIN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛米羅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果出生的國度不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:02:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會有這樣溫和的神情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利茲  你怎麼還在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要去墨西哥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在我不在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你在這乖一點  以作為對國家作出的貢獻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得他很帥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真分不清東亞人的臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概只知道他的樣子很悠閒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這個孩子能殺人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副連螞蟻也不會踩死的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你也這麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刀既是武器又是盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:02:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以小刀為武器的對戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把敵人小刀彈開的瞬間  就分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手下留情了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手還拿著刀子  勒住對手又能怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}本日下午  在墨西哥蒂華納發現了FBI調查官布萊斯的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用眼睛和耳朵記住語言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}當局由現場的情況判斷是他殺  並開始調查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}布萊斯在調查一個以南美為據點的恐怖集團——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}諾切·德·桑古雷在美國國內的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}這次的事件也被認為和諾切·德·桑古雷有一定的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去殺人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei的完成度怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術面上已經接近完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein  過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也…無法識破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這白皙而柔軟的肌膚掩蓋著如此危險的凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿起它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我孕育出的  我製造出的完美的素材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓這種完美永遠地延續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Zwei完成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使他像你一樣完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了使你完成的最後的校訂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein  把你的完美傳到下一代給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein  這次很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須準備一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我等到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你們組織是多麼重要你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長年冒著危險為你們走私軍火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你的功績表示敬意  沃列斯大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是多少有點突然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在休假期間被捲入了殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是災難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺的好像是FBI調查官的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼  被懷疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受審的話  你們的處境也一樣危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno有照顧我的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個小時後  你將會看到加勒比海的黎明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑一支你覺得到現在為止用得最熟的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是訓練？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  今晚是考試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該到飛機場去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底想怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬格維雅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是美國海軍的沃列斯大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是大型的自動手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你們到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太貪得無厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只和我們交易的話  事情也不會敗露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  你就連恐怖份子也作為武器走私的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因此被FBI盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno以秘密的維持為鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃列斯大尉  Inferno為你準備了自救手段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你的時間是從現在起10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我們將派人過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能逃掉的話就算是你的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個建築物裡有武器庫  請便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是給你一個讓你以自己的力量贏取生命與自由的機會而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是軍人的老本行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是對我的報酬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這也算…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有能浪費的時間吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你聽到的一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei  給你第一個任務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了那男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你用什麼手段  幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等  我還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹得很好  非常優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以安心讓你上戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉世無雙的Inferno的Phantom都如此認同了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更自信些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信…哪有什麼殺人的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去  Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再給你一次選擇的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要接受一切活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是拒絕一切死去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手可是現役的海豹突擊隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以請馬格維雅先生大駕光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想讓您親眼見證他的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底拿了什麼武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤的時候要站在逃跑的立場上思考
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑時則反過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最先想到的  對手也一樣想到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom  你覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃列斯大尉是接受過訓練的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實戰經驗也比Zwei豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要拋棄雜念  Zwei的反應速度和集中能力更勝一籌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結論呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五五開  剩下的要看雙方的潛在能力決定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei的勝算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道沃列斯大尉的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有武器了  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不知道為什麼像你這樣的孩子會被迫幹這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你好好考慮考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你沒有理由互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個比我小多了的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:16:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓弟弟過上寬裕的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要見到一隻老鼠就是有三十隻在那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了一次謊話的人就會說一大堆謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直走在獨木橋上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓他上了大學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起碼也要照顧他到畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專家會帶著多種工具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺手也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你都是被Inferno利用了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是那個組織
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為兩槍之內  已經足以分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那個少年輸了  我們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精彩的餘興節目必須一步一步來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一  您在車裡等候如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的傢伙我見多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連扳機都不敢扣的膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就教教你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人可不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都能辦到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看殺人  課程才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為第一次你幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  這應該是做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這夢很長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夢的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你沒死去或者發狂前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會醒的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這由你決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄你的眼睛  你的耳朵  你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後化作一個Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬事都用Zwei的眼睛去看  用Zwei的耳朵去聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣  就不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再悲傷  變得輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不叫Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來  Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪找到那少年的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從日本的一個管道推薦來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  在那種安樂的國家也隱藏著能人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試合格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來你就是Inferno的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.16,0:23:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告  暗殺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是過去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的絕望和痛苦我都知道
